org.dice_research.squirrel.metadata

Class CrawlingActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dice_research.squirrel.metadata.CrawlingActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CrawlingActivity
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Representation of Crawling activity. A crawling activity is started by a single worker, and sends this data to the sink. So, it contains a bunch of Uris and some meta data, like timestamps for the start and end of the crawling activity.
